text: My first coloring app and prolly last too since I don't see the need to download other apps when this works excellently! üòÄüëç I wasn't really into coloring and only tried this because I was looking for apps to have fun with my stylus but I had more fun than I expected.  Lots of patterns and color palletes to choose from and has got nice features without distracting ads. Great app, indeed!

Wow! This coloring app is truly amazing. Tried a few other coloring apps, but personally ColorMe tops all of them. The app is free and you can color a variety of things. My favorite to do is the mandalas. It's worth all of my spare time and it's very relaxing- stress relieving as well. Good job Adults Coloring Books. ‚ò∫ I am definitely keeping this app. üòÄ

This is my first coloring app. I got it due to the review of variety, ease of use, variety, lack of adds, and all pages are actually free.  I was disappointed that it wasn't more like actual coloring where you can pick coloring tool and shade, but I downloaded others that I immediately deleted. Maybe this will help me build to others -this is definitely a good start -that will take me a while  there are tons of pics!

Best coloring app in the whole app store! I play this app whenever I have  time. ‚è∞ (Witch is most of the time when I'm not playing my other games!) This is a great app, good for relaxing and I love that its free and there's no ads! Plus, there are so many options to chose from. Including animals, faces, flowers, mandalas, owls, and more! One more thing.. Its good cause u can save ur drawing and continue on them. Or delete them and start new! Highly recomend!
replyText: Thank you for such a lovely review

text: I love the fact that there is such a huge range of things to colour in and you don't have to pay to download other categories! Not to mention there is so many different colours and 100% ad free!  Best app I've used/downloaded so far. :)

Good selection of drawings. Not super fond of the layout of the program. For instance the colors disappear when you are drawing. I like how it saves the last 3 colors so you know which you used last. Wish they had some really bright neon colors. Tgank yiu for making a free coloring app! Would recommend

This is the best app I have!! It's relaxing as hell and UNLIKE ALL OTHER COLORING APPS, it's free!! If you check other coloring apps they charged ridiculously crazy prices for JUST different colors! Also new pages to color cost too! NO ADDS OR CONSTANT REQUEST TO SPEND MONEY!! This is a must have as long as it stays free

I have ADHD and severe anxiety and this app is just like medication, It's my colouring meditation! You just have to try it, coz until you do, you are seriously missing out on one of the most amazing apps in a generation! 10/10 Thanks for making this wonderful app üôÇ

Unlike every other app for coloring, it is ENTIRELY free. No premium palettes or designs. And there are lots of fun designs. They need some assistance in their design department, but for free, it is amazing!!  Edit: The designs that I thought were simple ended up being much more involved. Props man. App is a great basic app to while a way the time. :)

I love this app! It is the third colouring app I have  gotten in the last 24 hours, and it is the absolute best! All the other colouring apps you either have to pay for full access or you get a pathetic amount of pictures. I have deleted the other two apps and am very satisfied.

It's great.. Especially when you are going through tough times it does take the stress away a bit.. So much selection of designs and a big range of colours.. No ads no needing to spend money it's great.. One thing though if there was a more bigger range of colours then this would be on top but other than that.. Amazing!

This is a nice time killer when you're bored. I enjoy playing this. The pictures are nice and there's also a wide range of colors. I'd recommend. Though I hope the creators can make more things to color. I think there should be full body portraits.

This app is fantastic for anyone who likes color and being a little creative. I have health issues and this takes my mind off of problems, as I get immediate results from the picture I am working on. Thanks so much!

No ads! And all the color options are great. I tried another coloring app and all the ads were annoying and the colors were limited. This app is the best I've found! I'd love a color mixer, but for free, I just can't complain about anything!

It's really helpful.  When i was downloading it, i was suffering from an attack (won't say what kind), but once i started playing, i calmed down.  Relaxing, addictive.  I could play for hours. And no ads to bug you while colouring. ‚ò∫   great game

Very well constructed app. Have been testing a lot of apps and usually the experience is not enjoyable at all. Too many ad intrusions, apps that really test your patience on an Android device. This one however is a keeper. Nice work Devs

This coloring app is the bes!  There are so many categories you can choose from!  There many different kinds of colors to use and choose!  I really enjoy this app.  It help me relieve my stress and helps pass time.

This is a great app and I am not pushed into a subscription commitment for $40 a year. I would be happy to pay a minimal fee for more coloring pages with additional upgrade fees. I just hate being locked in to an app subscription.
It's very addicting and pulls the inner artist out. I get to play with so many different combinations of color! I hope they put out more pictures soon!
replyText: Donquel, thank you for amazing review

text: Beautiful patterns and a wide range of pretty colours to choose from - for free! It is easy to use and you can use the same pattern more than once for different colour ways. So far, no annoying ads or being pestered to upgrade for a fee. Where's the catch? (I haven't found one yet, so am upping my review to 5 stars üåü)

This is a great app.  It never glitches.  It gives so many pictures and colors to use, unlike some of the other free coloring apps. Great for long waits at the doctors office, or car trips.  My 8 year old grandson loves it too.

Best apps so far.. Hey guys. Since u are very responsive to comment, may i suggest that when we hover on a colour, it stated what color it is, that feature will really benificial for a partially colorblind people like me.

Fantastic coloring app! Definitely relaxing to do and the images range from quite a lot (human faces, flowers, animals, etc) I really enjoy variety. Only giving 4 stars because sometimes I close the app by mistake and my coloring image is not saved AT ALL. That sucks because the color scheme I use is so unique it's hard to remember it. Also, it'd be nice to have a recent colors section instead of the just two recent ones.
replyText: Odallys thanks for great feedback and advice. We¬¥re working on it.

text: It is fun and calming and it is just amazing. A fun mediation but not quite perfect. You can't find a small picture that is easy. And there is only one way to paint the picture.There should be more than one paintbrush
This is a fun little app exactly what you would expect. It had no ads that I could see. I don't know about the stress relief part but I guess any distracting thing could reduce stress.

Awesome. Super fun and relaxing. There are so many beautiful pictures to color in with a large variety of colors. You can really let your imagination fly when you use this app because there are so many things you can do with it. Other colorin apps don't have nearly the content of this app.

Brilliant  Omg I love it.. The pictures are brilliant and free..wow.. Best one I've downloaded by far.. Only thing is there are no different types of colour..like pearlised, metallics..but it in no way decreases this brilliant colouring app..it would just improve it..
replyText: Clare thanks for wonderful feedback. We¬¥re working on it.

text: As someone who loves to paint, this is a stunning app. It is easier for those who hate the fact that their outline drawing isn't perfect on paper. It also helps with creativity in colouring. Its relaxing and so addictive. So happy I downloaded this app.
Love interface, categories, & pics. Terrible selection of Colors (too limited)! Adding lots more colors would make at least a 4 üåü! Could be great & perfect for rehabilitation.

text: I really like the app and coloring over all. It is very relaxing and good selection. The only reason I knocked one star is because very common main colors are missing from the pallet. Needs more colors to be 5 star.
App is great but I would like a help screen. When you open coloring page how do you go back to another drawing without exiting the program other than that it's a great great app
replyText: Barbara thanks for review and your advice :) we'll take a look at it

text: Great app, but the color pallet doesnt stay on the screen in the Android the same way it stays on the screen in an iPad.  Annoying that I have to open the pallet to see the color choices.

Very nice! A lack of designs in certain categories, however, and I'd like to be able to do designs again without redoing them. Also, there's kind of a lack of colour choices. Overall, however, It's a brilliant app!
Terrific. Really feels like I'm colouring in for real and I love the images. The only thing is maybe I'm missing something but shouldn't there be a button to save your picture?
It has great colours and I love how it's all free. Other colouring apps I used had loads of things that cost money and very little free colour palletes. I hope new colours and pictures come soon.
replyText: Lucia, thank you for gorgeous review

text: Useless app, it doesn't work. I've tried everything to get a colour to add to a design and no result.
Not happy everytime I add coloring to a design then leave and return it doesn't keep the new changes, so I have to start over again.  It's a waste of my time.
Super relaxing and unwinding especially with my ocd tendencies. Feeling in control. And theres so many pages to choose from!
